    "The evaluation for each sampled architecture then acts as the signal to adjust the selections.",
    "That is, there is a decision maker who memorizes the prior results of previous architecture choices and analyzes the prior results to give the next recommended choice.",
    "The emergent LLMs have excellent memorization and reasoning capabilities that would work for automated learning.",
    "Several works have attempted to validate the potential of automated machine learning with LLMs.",
    "Preliminarily, GPT-NAS [193] takes advantage of the generative capability of LLMs."
